```

It also renders `INFO_environment.deployment=blue` as the following:

```
{
  "environment": {
    "deployment": "blue"
  },
  "app": {
    "version": {
      "spring": "4.3.3.RELEASE",
      "java": "1.8.0_111"
    }
  }
…
